root: ^Dylan's mother: "I hate the way you always have to have the last say in things."
^Dylan's father: "It got difficult to put up with you always thinking you're right."
^Dylan's father: "And not to mention, you only listen to respond. You're not actually hearing me."
^Dylan's mother: "You only listen to fish for chances to fire back at me."
^Dylan: "Uh oh! Looks like they're fighting again! Let's head over quick!"
